0382   E0E3 D0 0C              BNE RS3A        ;START AND INITIALIZE EVERYTHING
0383   E0E5 AD 57 E7           LDA INTAB3+1
0384   E0E8 CD 03 A4           CMP NMIV2+1
0385   E0EB D0 04              BNE RS3A
